///// windows ///////////////////////////////////////////////

1. install python (https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.9.1/python-3.9.1-amd64.exe)
2. install java (https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/AutoDL?BundleId=243737_61ae65e088624f5aaa0b1d2d801acb16)
3. download portable chrome (https://chromium.woolyss.com/) and extract to Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/chrome
3. download repository (https://github.com/bartol/amadeus2.hr/archive/master.zip)
4. extract repository/dashboard to Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/code
5. cd in code dir and run C:\> python -m venv venv
6. C:\> pip install -r requirements.txt
7. edit config.ini file, edit win/gui.bat
8. create Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/data/{table,update}, Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/cache, Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/logs
9. create shortcut to gui.bat, update.bat on Desktop
10. add update.bat to task scheduler (every 30 mins)
